          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1480674310" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17445678688504882479"><br/><img src='https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1380315844ra/689211.gif' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/><br/><br/>Description: <i>This is a rhyming story of a mouse and a monster. Little mouse goes for a walk in a dangerous forest. To scare off his enemies he invents tales of a fantastical creature called the Gruffalo. So imagine his surprise when he meets the real Gruffalo.</i><br/><br/><img src='https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1451168426i/17513262._SX540_.jpg' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/><br/><br/>4* The Stick Man<br/>5* The Gruffalo</span>
