<li class='cover' id='bookCover_201126'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/201126.We_re_Going_on_a_Bear_Hunt"><img alt="We&#39;re Going on a Bear Hunt" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1388274854l/201126._SX98_.jpg" />
